name: Login test

children.description: Given the user is on the demoblaze page
Actor opens the browser at https://www.demoblaze.com/

When user enters credentials
| user | pass |
| MatteoSierra | mateosierra |
Then the user should see a "Welcome MatteoSierra" message
Then valiate tex t$ byte buddy$ ny n icu ci should be a string containing 'Welcome MatteoSierra'
